using Flow
    installation
        check the flow version in the bottom of the .flowconfig file and run the below command
            yarn add flow-bin@0.33.0 --dev  (change the version number with the version found above)
        add below line inside the scripts on package.json file
            "flow": "flow",
            "flow-stop": "flow stop‚Äù
        flow reference - https://medium.com/react-native-training/getting-started-with-react-native-and-flow-d40f55746809


using eslint
    installation
        install needed dev packages
            yarn add eslint eslint-config-airbnb eslint-plugin-import eslint-plugin-react eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y babel-eslint --dev
        In windows 
            node node_modules\eslint\bin\eslint.js --init
        In mac 
            eslint --init
        eslint reference - https://github.com/airbnb/javascript/issues/1589

Runing android on mac
    chmod 755 android/gradlew

